<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٨٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5983">‌مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يَحْيَى </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/16361">‌إِبْرَاهِيمُ بْنُ زِيَادٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/50">‌إِبْرَاهِيمُ بْنُ سَعْدٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2287">‌أَبِيهِ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ نَحْوَهُ وَقَالَ: <span class="c2">«وَسُورَةٍ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>